        <h2>Who Is BetterHelp Best For?</h2>
        <p>BetterHelp is a strong choice if you:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Want <strong>flexibility</strong> — therapy on your schedule, not a therapist's</li>
          <li>Prefer <strong>text-based communication</strong> and don't want to do video calls</li>
          <li>Live in a <strong>regional area</strong> with limited local therapist access</li>
          <li>Want to <strong>switch therapists easily</strong> if the fit isn't right</li>
          <li>Have a <strong>moderate budget</strong> — it's more affordable than private in-person therapy</li>
        </ul>

